  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, home prices in Santa Clara, CA, can vary significantly based on factors such as location, property size, and market conditions. Generally, the median home prices in Santa Clara have been known to range from around $1 million to over $1.5 million for single-family homes, while condos and townhomes might be priced lower, often between $600,000 and $1 million.\n\nFor the most current and accurate information on home prices, I recommend checking real estate websites like Zillow, Realtor.com, or local real estate listings, as market conditions can change frequently.",
